1.3.3.name: wordpress/photoshelter-gallery-widget
1.3.3.description: The PhotoShelter Gallery Widget is a plugin for WordPress that allows photographers to easily display the latest photo or photos from any number of their public PhotoShelter galleries. This plugin doesn't show galleries in collections. PhotoShelter is web application used by photographers around the world use to sell and license images.
